title: No. 5 Hokies clinch program record, eighth ACC series - VT hokiesports.com
content: No. 5 Hokies clinch program record, eighth ACC series  VT hokiesports.com
description: Backed by third-year outfielder Gavin Cross swinging three hits on Sunday, the No. 5 Virginia Tech baseball team clinched its record-setting eighth ACC series of the season as the Hokies outlasted No. 7 Louisville, 6-4, at English Field at Atlantic Union Bank Park.
